sources.title: Leather Jacket Jungle / Teenage Gang Debs (1966, Crime) by Sande N. Johnsen | Movie
sources.description:
They all talk, fight and love just one way--DIRTY!
A no-good Manhattan girl moves in on a Brooklyn gang. Using her obvious charms she gets the leader killed in a fight over her and then takes up with the victor and new head man. Then she starts pushing him to get out onto the streets to mix it with rival gangs.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/TtW-At6_4yE


Original title: Teenage Gang Debs (1966) AKA: Leather Jacket Jungle

This film is subtitled in many language options.

Director: Sande N. Johnsen
Writers: Hy Cahl, William Shakespeare (uncredited)
Stars: Diane Conti (as Terry the Lady Macbeth character), Linda Gale, Eileen Dietz
Genres:  Classics, Crime, Literary
